{"tid":1486503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】不滿港鐵無回應訴求 有車長今自發罷工","createTime":"2019-08-19T01:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T01:43:41.000Z","uid":56881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96a00d24e8e4803edd130f8789ec9a884ed740a6","tid":1486503,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%84%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-000900266.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5-000900266.html&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsmWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=fe73a203\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%84%A1%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%9C%89%E8%BB%8A%E9%95%B7%E4%BB%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-000900266.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XHfsPbCvUw9lXYI1Hnkp9g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190819a081022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXHfsPbCvUw9lXYI1Hnkp9g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190819a081022.jpg&h=f8a1b6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n資料圖片。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】早前有逾700名港鐵車長及員工實名聯署，不滿警方多次在車站內發射催淚彈，令前線員工安全受到嚴重威脅，要求港鐵不應盲目配合警方。有聯署的港鐵車長表示，由於至今未得到港鐵管理層回應，決定將行動升級，呼籲所有車長今日（19日）自發「靜坐不上車」或「請假不上班」抗議，要求港鐵正視訴求。<br />\n<br />\n有份聯署的港鐵資深車長、葵青區區議員梁志成昨日表示，今次活動沒有大台，抗議方式將分為「靜坐不上車」及「請假不上班」，預料約200名車長參與。據他了解，港鐵已經啟動後備機制，一旦有車長拒絕執行職務，便會安排其他車長代替。他又指，已經以區議員身份去信運輸及房屋局局長陳帆，要政府確保港鐵員工及乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n聯署要求港鐵回應員工訴求，包括譴責及追究警方在車站範圍進行妄顧安全的驅散、全面及深層清潔車站內的化學殘留物質，安排專家測量車站內的通風系統空氣品質，並向市民公佈數據等。<br />\n<br />\n車長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aecdd170b045601c2b129d60da2a927161800eab","tid":1486503,"uid":245784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}